 Object>> entrySet() {\n            return delegate.entrySet();\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 958, "output": 997, "cacheRead": 20992, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 22947, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780902089405, "responseId": "resp_03b0256f7f04ed56016a2668c9d958819790f98b7aaf1e7270"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_61p0j0wgNt5vcehgyTVTJxZK|fc_03b0256f7f04ed56016a2668d1b12881978d21587532077f1d", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 3170 bytes to tests/src/velocity/velocity/1.5/src/test/java/velocity/velocity/MapSetExecutorTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780902104662}]}
